  "texts": [
    "Recommendations for ensuring user privacy and data protection in virtual worldsEnsuring user privacy and data protection is paramount in the virtual worlds of the Metaverse, where AI technologies collect and analyse vast amounts of user data.",
    "To safeguard user privacy and maintain trust within virtual environments, the following recommendations are essential:1.",
    "Adopt privacy-by-design principles in the development of AI systems and virtual environments [17].",
    "This approach involves integrating privacy protections into the very design and architecture of AI applications, ensuring that privacy is considered from the outset rather than retrofitted as an afterthought [87]. 2.",
    "Provide users with clear and accessible options to control the collection and use of their personal data."
  ],
